('w_environment_A2_06','protect','/prəˈtɛkt/','verb','보호하다','To keep someone or something safe from harm.','We need to {protect} our oceans.','우리는 바다를 보호해야 해요.','protect','A2','environment',1,'protect nature wildlife shield green'),
('w_environment_A2_07','reduce','/rɪˈdjuːs/','verb','줄이다','To make something smaller in size, amount, or degree.','Let''s {reduce} the amount of plastic we use.','플라스틱 사용량을 줄여요.','reduce','A2','environment',1,'reduce waste less eco lifestyle'),
('w_environment_A2_08','reuse','/ˌriːˈjuːz/','verb','재사용하다','To use something again.','I always {reuse} my shopping bags.','저는 항상 장바구니를 재사용해요.','reuse','A2','environment',1,'reuse bag bottle green eco'),
('w_environment_A2_09','plastic','/ˈplæstɪk/','noun','플라스틱','A light, strong material made from chemicals.','Avoid single-use {plastic} products.','일회용 플라스틱 제품을 피해요.','plastic','A2','environment',1,'plastic bottle bag pollution waste'),
('w_environment_A2_10','garbage','/ˈɡɑːrbɪdʒ/','noun','쓰레기','Things that are no longer useful and are thrown away.','Please put your {garbage} in the bin.','쓰레기를 통에 버려주세요.','garbage','A2','environment',1,'garbage trash bin rubbish waste'),
('w_environment_A2_11','electric','/ɪˈlɛktrɪk/','adjective','전기의','Powered by electricity.','An {electric} car produces no exhaust fumes.','전기차는 배기가스를 배출하지 않아요.','electric','A2','environment',1,'electric car vehicle green energy'),
('w_environment_A2_12','smoke','/smoʊk/','noun','연기','The grey or black gas produced when something burns.','Factory {smoke} pollutes the air.','공장 연기가 공기를 오염시켜요.','smoke','A2','environment',1,'smoke factory pollution air dark'),
('w_environment_A2_13','toxic','/ˈtɒksɪk/','adjective','유독한','Poisonous and harmful.','The factory released {toxic} chemicals into the river.','공장이 강에 유독한 화학물질을 방류했어요.','toxic','A2','environment',1,'toxic poison chemical waste danger'),
('w_environment_A2_14','litter','/ˈlɪtər/','verb','쓰레기를 버리다','To throw waste carelessly in a public place.','Please don''t {litter} in the park.','공원에 쓰레기를 버리지 마세요.','litter','A2','environment',1,'litter trash street pollution waste'),
('w_environment_A2_15','save','/seɪv/','verb','절약하다, 구하다','To keep something for future use or to prevent waste.','Remember to {save} water every day.','매일 물을 절약하는 걸 기억해요.','save','A2','environment',1,'save water energy eco green'),
('w_environment_A2_16','natural','/ˈnætʃərəl/','adjective','자연적인','Existing in or produced by nature.','Use {natural} cleaning products at home.','집에서 천연 세정제를 사용해요.','natural','A2','environment',1,'natural organic eco product green'),
('w_environment_A2_17','resource','/ˈriːsɔːrs/','noun','자원','Something available to use or be used for a purpose.','Water is a precious {resource}.','물은 소중한 자원이에요.','resource','A2','environment',1,'resource water energy land eco'),
('w_environment_A2_18','damage','/ˈdæmɪdʒ/','noun','피해, 손상','Physical harm that reduces value or usefulness.','Pollution causes serious {damage} to the environment.','오염은 환경에 심각한 피해를 줘요.','damage','A2','environment',1,'damage destruction pollution nature harm'),
('w_environment_A2_19','dirty','/ˈdɜːrti/','adjective','더러운','Not clean; containing or covered with harmful substances.','The river looks very {dirty} near the factory.','공장 근처의 강이 매우 더러워 보여요.','dirty','A2','environment',1,'dirty river pollution water waste'),
('w_environment_A2_20','plant','/plænt/','verb','심다','To put a seed or plant in the ground so it will grow.','Let''s {plant} more trees this weekend.','이번 주말에 나무를 더 심어요.','plant','A2','environment',1,'plant tree garden seed grow'),
('w_environment_A2_21','light bulb','/laɪt bʌlb/','noun','전구','A glass container that produces light when electricity passes through it.','Switch to LED {light bulbs} to save energy.','에너지 절약을 위해 LED 전구로 바꿔요.','light bulb','A2','environment',1,'light bulb LED energy saving electric'),
