('w_environment_C2_10','technosphere','/ˈtɛknoʊsfɪər/','noun','기술권','The sphere of human-made objects and infrastructure on Earth.','The growing {technosphere} is a geological force in its own right.','성장하는 기술권은 그 자체로 하나의 지질학적 힘이에요.','technosphere','C2','environment',1,'technosphere technology human infrastructure earth'),
('w_environment_C2_11','stratospheric aerosol injection','/ˌstrætəˈsfɛrɪk ˈɛərəsɒl ɪnˈdʒɛkʃən/','noun phrase','성층권 에어로졸 주입','Injecting particles into the stratosphere to reflect sunlight.','{Stratospheric aerosol injection} could rapidly cool the planet.','성층권 에어로졸 주입은 지구를 빠르게 냉각시킬 수 있어요.','stratospheric aerosol injection','C2','environment',1,'stratospheric aerosol injection sky cool geoengineering'),
